{"id": "ChIJPYZJ29DbwoARnAYWnOojI5s", "rating": 4.8, "priceLevel": "PRICE_LEVEL_INEXPENSIVE", "userRatingCount": 273, "displayName": {"text": "626 Ice Cream", "languageCode": "en"}, "editorialSummary": {"text": "Open since 1990, this casual storefront offers a range of flavors of straightforward frozen yogurt.", "languageCode": "en"}, "reviews": [{"name": "places/ChIJPYZJ29DbwoARnAYWnOojI5s/reviews/Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT2xwaFJYWmxNbkJHVmpkS1ZXZElkakU1YkdGWk5rRRAB", "relativePublishTimeDescription": "4 weeks ago", "rating": 5, "text": {"text": "If you're visiting from out of town, 626 is a MUST GO. I can't emphasize enough how kind the staff is. Matea immediately made me feel welcome to sample one of every flavor. The rest of the team thoughtfully walked me through all the topping options and offered to put them on the side for me so I can experiment with new things. The mood lighting, music, and availability of seating really throw 626 FAR beyond any other ice cream experience I've had in DC/Baltimore.", "languageCode": "en"}, "originalText": {"text": "If you're visiting from out of town, 626 is a MUST GO. I can't emphasize enough how kind the staff is. Matea immediately made me feel welcome to sample one of every flavor. The rest of the team thoughtfully walked me through all the topping options and offered to put them on the side for me so I can experiment with new things. The mood lighting, music, and availability of seating really throw 626 FAR beyond any other ice cream experience I've had in DC/Baltimore.", "languageCode": "en"}, "authorAttribution": {"displayName": "Jyoti Singhal", "uri": "https://www.google.com/maps/contrib/111599847084991387824/reviews", "photoUri": "https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWLrjb0LT_h3SXsd73BfdS-ZDi7GEzuMER7Qya1V4-JEMkTz0t-zQ=s128-c0x00000000-cc-rp-mo"}, "publishTime": "2026-06-15T05:54:05.739116163Z", "flagContentUri": "https://www.google.com/local/content/rap/report?postId=Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT2xwaFJYWmxNbkJHVmpkS1ZXZElkakU1YkdGWk5rRRAB&d=17924085&t=1", "googleMapsUri": "https://www.google.com/maps/reviews/data=!4m6!14m5!1m4!2m3!1sCi9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT2xwaFJYWmxNbkJHVmpkS1ZXZElkakU1YkdGWk5rRRAB!2m1!1s0x80c2dbd0db49863d:0x9b2323ea9c16069c"}, {"name": "places/ChIJPYZJ29DbwoARnAYWnOojI5s/reviews/Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT21oT2RYRlBSRnB1YzB4RFUyODNNRzFGWmpkMVJVRRAB", "relativePublishTimeDescription": "a month ago", "rating": 3, "text": {"text": "I really truly believed I was going to love this spot… if not due to the unanimously rave reviews, or due to the highly curated vibes, then at least to justify the long line at 9pm to myself. Everything feels intentional - the crossword puzzle posted outside for folks to pass the time, the extra stools in the parking lot, the mood lighting, the games available, and the extremely friendly staff that explain every single flavor and encourage you to sample it all.\n\nUnfortunately it’s the ice cream that matters at the end of the day. It’s def more like a froyo which really threw me off as I was expecting soft serve ice cream. The flavors tasted true to their names but didn’t taste right as an ice cream. We tried everything they had still available and went with the yakult in the end since it was the most like a tangy froyo. The cups are pricey for the size and small amount of toppings. I’d be annoyed if I drove out of my way to come here and wait in that line.", "languageCode": "en"}, "originalText": {"text": "I really truly believed I was going to love this spot… if not due to the unanimously rave reviews, or due to the highly curated vibes, then at least to justify the long line at 9pm to myself. Everything feels intentional - the crossword puzzle posted outside for folks to pass the time, the extra stools in the parking lot, the mood lighting, the games available, and the extremely friendly staff that explain every single flavor and encourage you to sample it all.\n\nUnfortunately it’s the ice cream that matters at the end of the day. It’s def more like a froyo which really threw me off as I was expecting soft serve ice cream. The flavors tasted true to their names but didn’t taste right as an ice cream. We tried everything they had still available and went with the yakult in the end since it was the most like a tangy froyo. The cups are pricey for the size and small amount of toppings. I’d be annoyed if I drove out of my way to come here and wait in that line.", "languageCode": "en"}, "authorAttribution": {"displayName": "Sarah Ky", "uri": "https://www.google.com/maps/contrib/101492518923056921744/reviews", "photoUri": "https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocJyll_xKFi25VeqFyBBrB02EW9YYV9dC9QEP9YGP3L8lWBsGQ=s128-c0x00000000-cc-rp-mo-ba4"}, "publishTime": "2026-06-04T02:43:43.406074469Z", "flagContentUri": "https://www.google.com/local/content/rap/report?postId=Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT21oT2RYRlBSRnB1YzB4RFUyODNNRzFGWmpkMVJVRRAB&d=17924085&t=1", "googleMapsUri": "https://www.google.com/maps/reviews/data=!4m6!14m5!1m4!2m3!1sCi9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT21oT2RYRlBSRnB1YzB4RFUyODNNRzFGWmpkMVJVRRAB!2m1!1s0x80c2dbd0db49863d:0x9b2323ea9c16069c"}, {"name": "places/ChIJPYZJ29DbwoARnAYWnOojI5s/reviews/Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT2pkek0yNUNka2MzYWtkS1lVSTBabTFZVmxwVFUwRRAB", "relativePublishTimeDescription": "2 months ago", "rating": 5, "text": {"text": "What a delightful and delicious surprise! We were out looking for some interesting ice cream and stumbled on this place.  6 flavors of soft serve. We both loved the Vietnamese Coffee! I got another flavor Yakukt (tart yogurt) and hubby got the coffee and condensed milk flavor.\n\nThe owner took the time to explain each flavor and give us a taste sample of 4 flavors.  For a Friday night it was packed and a line out the door,  but totally worth it. Great vibes inside!", "languageCode": "en"}, "originalText": {"text": "What a delightful and delicious surprise! We were out looking for some interesting ice cream and stumbled on this place.  6 flavors of soft serve. We both loved the Vietnamese Coffee! I got another flavor Yakukt (tart yogurt) and hubby got the coffee and condensed milk flavor.\n\nThe owner took the time to explain each flavor and give us a taste sample of 4 flavors.  For a Friday night it was packed and a line out the door,  but totally worth it. Great vibes inside!", "languageCode": "en"}, "authorAttribution": {"displayName": "Lisa Cumes", "uri": "https://www.google.com/maps/contrib/103850446424788931282/reviews", "photoUri": "https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUYbCwwX5LRTfViChYAI_ul7U7dOwPZ6lwRcxHvtaKEdMGc_ymqow=s128-c0x00000000-cc-rp-mo-ba2"}, "publishTime": "2026-05-02T03:57:22.192259553Z", "flagContentUri": "https://www.google.com/local/content/rap/report?postId=Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT2pkek0yNUNka2MzYWtkS1lVSTBabTFZVmxwVFUwRRAB&d=17924085&t=1", "googleMapsUri": "https://www.google.com/maps/reviews/data=!4m6!14m5!1m4!2m3!1sCi9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT2pkek0yNUNka2MzYWtkS1lVSTBabTFZVmxwVFUwRRAB!2m1!1s0x80c2dbd0db49863d:0x9b2323ea9c16069c"}, {"name": "places/ChIJPYZJ29DbwoARnAYWnOojI5s/reviews/ChZDSUhNMG9nS0VJQ0FnTUR3NzdTOVBnEAE", "relativePublishTimeDescription": "a year ago", "rating": 5, "text": {"text": "This is actually an incredible ice cream shop. The first thing you notice is the fantastic vibe, lots of cool decorations in a dimly lit setting that makes it super chill to hang out at night. They only have a handful of flavors all of which are delicious. There are also lots of toppings to choose from that add that little extra to the ice cream. Staff are super friendly and helpful, the samples are also much larger than most other ice cream shops. Overall a really great place to hang out for ice cream.", "languageCode": "en"}, "originalText": {"text": "This is actually an incredible ice cream shop. The first thing you notice is the fantastic vibe, lots of cool decorations in a dimly lit setting that makes it super chill to hang out at night. They only have a handful of flavors all of which are delicious. There are also lots of toppings to choose from that add that little extra to the ice cream. Staff are super friendly and helpful, the samples are also much larger than most other ice cream shops. Overall a really great place to hang out for ice cream.", "languageCode": "en"}, "authorAttribution": {"displayName": "Shawn Sheng", "uri": "https://www.google.com/maps/contrib/105985962205417329267/reviews", "photoUri": "https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocJLfF1ACfIP4bZk8Sg5fvSBwPmeOx26fpTh6PjpxMmqZZ70XQ=s128-c0x00000000-cc-rp-mo-ba6"}, "publishTime": "2025-03-29T04:28:36.079946Z", "flagContentUri": "https://www.google.com/local/content/rap/report?postId=ChZDSUhNMG9nS0VJQ0FnTUR3NzdTOVBnEAE&d=17924085&t=1", "googleMapsUri": "https://www.google.com/maps/reviews/data=!4m6!14m5!1m4!2m3!1sChZDSUhNMG9nS0VJQ0FnTUR3NzdTOVBnEAE!2m1!1s0x80c2dbd0db49863d:0x9b2323ea9c16069c"}, {"name": "places/ChIJPYZJ29DbwoARnAYWnOojI5s/reviews/Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT25ScFNFSm1TVEZuUmxoNFluUTJSSHBYZVc1QlRHYxAB", "relativePublishTimeDescription": "2 months ago", "rating": 4, "text": {"text": "Interesting place that is very hip. Asian American style ice cream, with favor like condensed milk, yakult, black sesame, Chinese rice cake etc… only open a few hours at night. Very friendly and Instagram style place", "languageCode": "en"}, "originalText": {"text": "Interesting place that is very hip. Asian American style ice cream, with favor like condensed milk, yakult, black sesame, Chinese rice cake etc… only open a few hours at night. Very friendly and Instagram style place", "languageCode": "en"}, "authorAttribution": {"displayName": "Howard H", "uri": "https://www.google.com/maps/contrib/110858322792321532702/reviews", "photoUri": "https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocLnFhDctic7F2Mnxwxl3GK1JOsEvb7124L7x9E-GxAFgJDvFFs=s128-c0x00000000-cc-rp-mo-ba5"}, "publishTime": "2026-04-22T16:54:39.211936640Z", "flagContentUri": "https://www.google.com/local/content/rap/report?postId=Ci9DQUlRQU